* Need to be able to add new categories and products, and enter reviews, benchmarks, and specs
* Categories
  * Schema:
    - name
* Manufacturers
  * Schema:
    - name
* Products
  * Schema:
    - belongs_to_related category
    - full name (just for easier access)
    - belongs_to_related manufacturer
    - chipset manufacturer id (used for video cards)
    - model name
    - summary of specs?
    - pros (text)
    - cons (text)
    - bottom line
    - market release date 
    - total avg price range info
    - total avg rating info
    - total avg benchmark index info
    - score / "experience index"
    - is_prototype (maybe we can ascertain this automatically)
    - embeds_many products
    - embeds_many reviews
    - embeds_many specs (hash, variant)
    - has_many_related benchmarks
    - embeds_many prices
    - embeds_many photos (array of Media)
* Benchmarks
  * Schema:
    - belongs_to_related product
    - belongs_to_related review (optional)
    - name
    - description
    - score
    - units
* Product reviews
  * Schema:
    - title
    - rating
    - pros
    - cons
    - bottom line
    - date
    - url
    - avg benchmark
    - has_many_related benchmarks
* Product specs
  * Schema:
    - gpu
    - shader model
    - directx
    - etc. 
* Product prices
  * Schema:
    - merchant
    - prices (array)
      - date
      - price
* Product photos
  * Schema:
    - url/filepath?
    - caption
* Need to be able to pull prices and photos automatically
  - Prices (Amazon, Newegg, Best Buy)
  - Photos (Amazon, Newegg)
